  "texts": [
    "Five databases (Medline, Embase, PsycInfo, Scopus and Web of Science) were electronically searched on 6 October 2023 for English language studies conducted prior to this date.",
    "Search strategies included text terms, MeSH terms and Boolean operators.",
    "Reference lists and citation searches were subsequently performed to identify sources not highlighted in these databases.",
    "PROSPERO was also searched for existing and ongoing systematic reviews on burnout in surgical trainees.",
    "Two protocols were identified on surgeon burnout; however, their aims, inclusion and exclusion criteria differed from this review."
  ],
